        "id": "MAKO_005_MAKO014B_012",
        "file": "voice/mako_005_mako014B_012.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「嗯啊啊！啊啊，啊啊～！呼啊啊，啊，啊，啊啊啊！」"
