      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_MAKO_H001A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_mako_h001a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "narration",
      "pages": [
        [
          "（啊啊啊，这全都……都被拍下来了！",
